{
  "title":"在 Google Maps 內多邊形取點 Point in Polygon",
  "at":"2015-11-26",
  "type":"article",
  "els":[
    {
      "e":"blockquote",
      "class": "warning",
      "t":"目前已將 Live Demo 關閉並且不維護囉，請大家先參考 GitHub 的原始碼吧！"
    },
    { "e":"p", "t":"這是項個人開發的工具，而且需要前後端配合一起弄的作品，主要目的是撈出藉由不規則多邊形範圍內的點座標。" },
    { "e":"img", "alt":"Demo 動畫", "src":"/img/dev/GoogleMaps-Point-in-Polygon/a7e1f952d0d539bd4a245f7e2aa524ea.gif" },
    { "e":"h2", "t":"前端" },
    {
      "e":"p",
      "s":[
        { "e":"span", "t":"主要是 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Google Maps JavaScript API v3", "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/?hl=zh-tw" },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 的地圖服務應用，利用 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Google Maps Marker", "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/markers" },
        { "e":"span", "t":"、" },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Google Maps Polyline", "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/examples/polyline-simple?hl=zh-tw" },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 去畫出一個不規則多邊形，並且利用 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Ajax", "href":"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/AJAX" },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 去後端撈取範圍內的 Marker，當 Ajax 傳回後端之前，先將該多邊形角的座標點利用 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"Google Maps LatLngBounds", "href":"https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/reference" },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 物件計算出多邊形的範圍(" },
        { "e":"b", "t":"東北" },
        { "e":"span", "t":"-" },
        { "e":"b", "t":"西南" },
        { "e":"span", "t":")座標，然後將範圍座標以及多邊形的角座標一併回傳給後端。" }
      ]
    },
    { "e":"h2", "t":"後端" },
    {
      "e":"p",
      "s":[
        { "e":"span", "t":"使用 " },
        { "e":"a", "t":"CodeIgniter", "href":"https://codeigniter.org.tw/" },
        { "e":"span", "t":" 最簡單的寫法，當接收到 Ajax 的 Request 之後，便開始撈資料。撈取資料的步驟拆成兩個步驟，首先利用範圍座標的東北-西南座標進 MySQL 撈出範圍內的點，此時的點是一個矩形範圍，所以需要再進入第二項的 filter 利用公式將多邊形外的點過濾掉，最後 Output 回去給前端即可。" }
      ]
    },
    { "e":"h2", "t":"小結" },
